Rating: 4
Very delicious! I served it for my book club and they loved it. I was able to put it together ahead of time and just put it in the oven prior to serving. Our book assignment was Shopgirl by Steve Martin. I selected this entree with a mango salad because the lead characters had their second date at Cha Cha Cha! The recipe is a keeper!

