Rating: 1
This dish was horrid! The dry and salty Ritz crackers ruined what looked like it might have been a good recipe. Don't waste your time or money on this one. I still get teased about my failed Carribean chicken dish. Some of my dinner guests reported having nightmares! So, have a Dionne Warwick moment and "Walk on By" this one. : )

Rating: 3
This is really great and easy to make in a hurry. It goes very nicely with rice and I have substituted the Ritz cracker crumbs with regular bread crumbs. Delicious and it is a "get dinner on the table quick" recipie.